<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='292111' id='t-292111'>if they weren't forced by society
into categories of either male or female</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='297477' id='t-297477'>the way South Africa used to force people
into categories of black or white.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='301778' id='t-301778'>We know from anthropological science
that race is fiction,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='305980' id='t-305980'>even though racism is very, very real,</span>
